{{#extend "layout"}}
    {{#content 'main'}}
        <div class="intro">
            <h1 class="page-title"> Keep The Holidays Happy </h1>
            <p class="intro-description">
                Stressed out about the political clash that will inevitably disrupt your thanksgiving dinner? <br />
                Let's prevent that from happening. Before Thursday, send a proposal to your family/friends and make it clear
                to them that you want to avoid any political discussion at the dinner table.
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-default btn-lg create-proposal"> Choose proposal </a>
            <div class="social-buttons">
                <a class="twitter-share-button"
                   href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http://www.keepholidayshappy.com
           &text=A+way+to+avoid+talking+about+politics+this+holiday+season
           &hashtags=KeepHolidaysHappy,SurvivalGuideToThanksgiving"
                   target="_blank">
                    <i class="icon-twitter icon"></i>
                </a>

                <a class="facebook-share"
                   href="https://www.facebook.com/dialog/share?app_id=145634995501895
           &display=popup&href=http%3A%2F%2Fkeepholidayshappy.com"
                   target="_blank">
                    <i class="icon-facebook icon"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="thanksgiving-table">

            <div class="table">
                <img src="images/marshmellow.svg" class="food marshmellows hidden-xs">
                <img src="images/cranberry.svg" class="food cranberry hidden-xs">
                <img src="images/potatoes.svg" class="food potatoes hidden-xs">
                <img src="images/turkey.svg" class="food turkey">
                <img src="images/wine.svg" class="food wine">
                <img src="images/gravy.svg" class="food gravy hidden-xs">
                <img src="images/pie.svg" class="food pie">

                <div class="stripe lg"></div>
                <div class="stripe md"></div>
                <div class="stripe sm"></div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!--SELECT TEMPLATE-->
        <div class="proposal-creator js-template-selection">

            <div class="how-to">
                <h3> Choose your proposal </h3>
                <p> Select a proposal below that you think will get through to your friends and family.
                    After selecting a proposal template, you can edit and send the proposal to your friends and family.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="btn-group template-options js-template-options hidden-xs">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default template-option js-template-option" data-template="template-1">No Trump at My Table</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default template-option js-template-option" data-template="template-2">No Need for World War 3</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default template-option js-template-option" data-template="template-3">Keep Your Feelings on Lock</button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default template-option js-template-option" data-template="template-4">Talk About Yourself Instead</button>

            </div>

            <select class="btn btn-default form-control visible-xs template-options-select">
                <option value="template-1">No Trump at My Table</option>
                <option value="template-2">No Need for World War 3</option>
                <option value="template-3">Keep Your Feelings on Lock</option>
                <option value="template-4">Talk About Yourself Instead</option>
            </select>

            <div class="proposal-container">
                <div class="proposal">
                    <textarea class="proposal-text js-proposal-textarea" rows="11"></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a class="btn btn-default btn-lg send-proposal" href="#">
                Select proposal
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="separator"></div>

        <!--CUSTOMISE ANSWER OPTIONS-->
        <div class="proposal-creator js-answer-options-edit">

            <div class="how-to">
                <h3> Customise it </h3>
                <p> That's how it will look to your friends. You can also choose what they can answer </p>
            </div>
            <div class="proposal-container">
                <div class="proposal">
                    <p class="proposal-text js-proposal-textarea">
                        Here goes the proposal from the 1st section. <br /><br />
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam aliquam suscipit massa. Sed
                        rhoncus leo in arcu ullamcorper, tempus pellentesque arcu finibus. Phasellus quis augue sed
                        metus mollis egestas. Vestibulum bibendum eros et orci pharetra interdum. Nam porttitor leo ut
                        ex gravida porta. Fusce ultrices, purus et blandit hendrerit, purus sem consequat quam, non
                        ornare sem purus sit amet lorem. Aenean rhoncus, odio id ullamcorper euismod, nisi ex tincidunt
                        ligula, quis rutrum eros sem a neque. Ut sollicitudin vel leo sit amet rutrum.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="template-options js-template-options hidden-xs">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default template-option js-XXX" data-template="template-1">
                    Yep! Sounds good to me
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default template-option js-XXX" data-template="template-2">
                    I can't promise anything
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default template-option js-XXX" data-template="template-3">
                    Nope, let the games begin!
                </button>

            </div>

            <div class="input-container js-buttons-input ">
                <h3>Edit answer options</h3>
                <div class="row answer-option-input">
                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                    <label class="control-label" for="btnAgree">"I agree" button: </label>
                </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="btnAgree" value="Yep! Sounds good to me">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row answer-option-input">
                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                        <label class="control-label" for="btnDontknow">"I don't know" button: </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="btnDontknow" value="I can't promise anything">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row answer-option-input">
                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                        <label class="control-label" for="btnDisagree">"I disagree" button: </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="btnDisagree" value="Nope, let the games begin!">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a class="btn btn-default btn-lg send-proposal" href="#">
                Add members
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="separator"></div>

        <!--ADD MEMBERS-->
        <div class="proposal-creator js-emails-input">

            <div class="how-to">
                <h3> Add members </h3>
                <p> Put your email and name and emails of your victims </p>
            </div>
            <div class="input-container ">
                <div class="row answer-option-input">
                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                        <label class="control-label" for="senderName">Your name </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="senderName" placeholder="That's how your proposal will be signed">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row answer-option-input">
                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                        <label class="control-label" for="senderEmail">Your email </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="senderEmail" placeholder="Answers to the proposals will be sent here">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3>Send it to</h3>
                <div class="row answer-option-input">
                    <div class="emails-list">
                        <span class="label label-email">mom@example.com  <a><i class="icon-cross icon"></i></a></span>
                        <span class="label label-email">dad@example.com  <a><i class="icon-cross icon"></i></a></span>
                        <span class="label label-email">grandma@example.com  <a><i class="icon-cross icon"></i></a></span>
                        <span class="label label-email">grandpa@example.com  <a><i class="icon-cross icon"></i></a></span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" >
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-3">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-add js-XXX" data-template="template-1">
                            Add email
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <img src="https://sophosnews.files.wordpress.com/2014/12/recaptcha_anchor2x.jpg?w=640" height="70px"/>
                </div>
            </div>


            <a class="btn btn-default btn-lg send-proposal" href="#">
                Send emails
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="separator"></div>

        <!--SUCCESS PAGE-->
        <div class="proposal-creator js-proposal-created">

            <div class="how-to">
                <h3> Successfully sent! </h3>
                <p> Your friends and family got your proposal. Follow the link below to see what they are answering.
                    We've also sent this link to your email.</p>
                <p></p><p></p>
                <p>Your tracking link:
                    <a href="#">keepholidayshappy.com/ghc34kgh345hg35h3g45k23g45k2hg45k2g45f2k5f</a></p>
                <p></p><p></p>
            </div>

        </div>
    {{/content}}
{{/extend}}
